==English==
/kownt-er klok-wize/

===Adverb===
'''counter-clockwise''' (''US'')
# Of movement, in a circular fashion so as to be moving to the left at the top of the [[circle]] and to the right at the bottom, in the opposite direction to the way the [[hand]]s of an [[analogue]]/[[analog]] [[clock]] move.

====Synonym====
*[[anticlockwise]] (''British'')

====Antonym====
*[[clockwise]]

